name: com.android.packageinstaller.television.UninstallAppProgress
description: This activity corresponds to a download progress screen that is displayed when an application is uninstalled. The result of the application uninstall is indicated in the result code that gets set to 0 or 1. The application gets launched by an intent with the intent's class name explicitly set to UninstallAppProgress and expects the application object of the application to uninstall.
